Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Got any plans for the end of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this festival and I was wondering if you'd like to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A festival for the end of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It'll be lots of fun! {added "yeah" - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it something like a snow festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to visit relatives...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...I received a similar invitation back during summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll translate what Konata said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants buddies to buy stuff for her at Comic Market.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was totally freaked out by the site when I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A festival's a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all work and no fun by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Izumi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm writing New Year's cards right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys in mourning and refusing cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't get a letter about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you absent one day this year because of a death in the family?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you used yet another trick out of manga!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiny shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the middle of cleaning right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When there's something you don't want to do, you suddenly want to clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...but once you start cleaning, it suddenly feels like a pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Less resting, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called Comiket?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it was a big festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it sure starts early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you haven't heard anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll get used to it soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...this event is gonna exhaust you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...in more than one way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! {added - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Picking up more and more of her people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll soon be allowed to enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is kinda scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I should explain your assignments now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Assignments?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,These are your shopping lists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we get inside, we'll split up and go around the circles according to this map.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You two handle 1-3 in the east building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take 4-6.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't follow the path marked in red...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...you might get stuck between rows of displays.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...and end up trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And here and here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're swept into the crowd there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'll be stuck for over half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to work so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones marked with green can wait until afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They're stocked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...so there's almost no danger of them running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just focus on the ones marked red before noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,S stands for something newly published.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,K stands for something already in print.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't know what's what, just buy everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have to pay in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The coffee will be your only refreshment for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a drink every thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be our final rendezvous point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,1 PM on the dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait fifteen minutes, but if you don't show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go look for you in the medical office, so watch the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You only ever sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...intelligent and passionate when this kind of stuff is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Climax from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The limit for new works is four copies per person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is A-92, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,One of each new book?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be 1,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what did you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of these are new...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The new ones would be this and this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one is 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy the snacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Three of each please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dripping Brigade Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Naughty Captain, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your total comes to 3,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your total is 4,500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Locked and loaded...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Onto the next point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the east building?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then north should be this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wa-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've pretty much covered all the big places.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:06:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The next place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a peek...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Gauron and Sousuke are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Too intense for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Legendary Girl A!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll think we're weird if we panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a weird jinx...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...where every circle suddenly becomes big after she buys a book! {Very circle?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we put so much effort into this book!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So she would buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it was the end of the year...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...we skipped work to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This year will be our year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We put a lot of work into the concert scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Iffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankssomuch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Next summer for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Pu-61 located?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't Pu in the east building?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the east building?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the west building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to go to the east building...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...get in that line there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...and go up one floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, probably an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I just now got back from the west building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You get completely lost after getting caught up in the crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...in this event...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to wait in line for an hour to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured it would be a rough schedule for a first-timer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...so let's just stroll around for the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it's gotten a lot better since they moved this to Ariake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They only had two convenience stores near the site at Harumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Site at Harumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The last one at Harumi was twelve years ago, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How old were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Around five?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad took me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We always stayed at this place called Hotel Urashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My first time was at the summer festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one crazy second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The sweat from all the participants evaporated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...and turned into these fluffy steam clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's gotten a lot easier after they moved this to Ariake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...but maybe it's 'cause of the people mainly here for events...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...many of the younger participants think of themselves as customers, sadly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This was supposed to be an event put on by all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt you while you're on a roll, but you've totally lost me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here during summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...but they also have places like these, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.55,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The main stuff is probably all sold out, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Nagato! Nagato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:43.40,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The person behind Nagamon is here as a salesgirl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.79,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be out of Haruhi goods!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I bother coming here if the Nagato phone cards are sold out!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:52.98,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.19,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.24,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:57.17,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm never coming back to this dump!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a spike in people like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, our limited goods...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...have already sold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're gonna show up this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:09.14,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you gotta line up early...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Asia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even customers who show up late...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...must be completely satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost the true spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have is leftover stuff now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Leftover, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Leftover items still have value!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A value that can't be found...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...in popular items and mainstream moe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This Comiket exists to reveal their true value!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that all limited goods have been eliminated,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the true battle has begun for industry booths!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,B-By George...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a recommendation to the customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dig up your true item!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything I can use as a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta be this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagato and everybody else is selling like hotcakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,yet look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Koizumi's sells well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's gone unsold for three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Captain's sold out instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, purchase this Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I recommend Sousuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wanted CoCo Saikoubi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,President Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...President Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I overheard your conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your desire to promote a new perspective of value is commendable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:44.72,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,That place is always pumped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:46.01,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.82,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot forgive your selfish desire to promote unpopular characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both main characters...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to help out at home as soon as we got back from Ariake...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do they have that event on New Year's Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You have an awful lot of energy for someone who was at that event since morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, it's cold so I figured you wouldn't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but January 1st is a new beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have to come charged up for the coming year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's what Dad said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, I'm disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrine maiden outfits are so invigorating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you guys do any praying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You were doing some intense praying, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go blabbing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't that intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was just hoping I could be in the same class as you and Miyuki this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami's actually pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You making fun of everything is why I never want to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's the way you resist...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong with that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan has always been the only one in a different class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Kuroi-sensei hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll also pray to be in the same class as Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami needs to be in a different class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That way I can borrow stuff from you when I forget mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't get caught if I copy your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're in our class, my rank will go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you go be in a different class by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The other...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:55.99,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Female students are so wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sebastian was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:15:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to draw your fortune this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Jigsy note: Not the Japanese quotes.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to get an early start on the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got to see something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be a good year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've already hit rock bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...things can only get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Something good will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It all depends on how you word it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to tie a bad luck ward on the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So many!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the power of bad luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether or not something good will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...depends on the amount of effort you spend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Drawing your fortune is just a game of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Although a staff member shouldn't be saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should go for a whole set from very good to very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they supposed to be trading cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can draw a secret fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What would a secret fortune be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Like ultra bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you go with something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody would want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever collects all of them gets a special item!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw a huge kagami mochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This big!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that where your name came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're not totally wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The round shape of a kagami mochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...is modeled after a mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's long been said that gods rest within mirrors,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so the name is supposed to invoke the blessings of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And the round shape also signifies family happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name has such a fantastic origin,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,yet she grew up to be an awfully pragmatic person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There sure are a lot of worshipers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's New Year's. {Maybe use "Because" instead of "Since" for a better flow.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, we aren't that well-known.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many of them are here for the shrine maidens like Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't that many!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have another wonderful year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this beautiful sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it fantastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all the pretty flowers everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to play a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some zoni soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he likes how I keep scurrying over until I get my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are really close, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I managed to get my money...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I'm planning on going to Gamers right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that all of those shops are in the city is a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already on a tight budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's the train fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish they'd open a shop near us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't a lot of stores sell online now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you could try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get points when you order online,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but browsing through the store and making unexpected discoveries is what's really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're totally ready to spend it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.57,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,The radishes are almost completely done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:15.72,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Now we'll put this completely in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why this is called a pochi bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's from the phrases pochitto (a smidge) and korepocchi (just a bit).
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It refers to a bag you put small stuff in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pochitto would be Kansai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...and korepocchi would be Kanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Takara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering where the name pochi bag came from...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.99,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Pochi bag, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you have a little more faith in your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:48.06,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I believe it came from the phrases pochitto and korepocchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And couldn't you do that somewhere out of sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.32,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,...and refers to a bag for small items.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to wish everyone in the game a happy new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:58.20,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(647,0)}and a mess and all. In the end, \NI wasn't able to buy any Haruhi goods...\N;_;\NDon't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{Spoken} It's Sensei.
