Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:15.43,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year, Sensei\NYo, Happy New Year! (^w^)/
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:17.68,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year, Sensei\NYo, Happy New Year! (^w^)/\NLet's have another wonderful year
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:21.69,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year, Sensei\NYo, Happy New Year! (^w^)/\NLet's have another wonderful year\NYep, sounds good (>w<)b
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{Spoken} And like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always online...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't she have anything else to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess that's why she doesn't have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Go-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Akira-sama's assistant, Shiraishi Minoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already on the twelfth episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This sea is hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama was supposed to appear in the actual show this week,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but she suddenly became ill...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A cold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I put up a cardboard pop-up instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...so if you go look carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...it looks like Akira-sama's already tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...so we'll have to call it a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm absolutely not getting full of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? {If this really is just "I'll" then it would be better to write it out. Although I guess it's connected with the next line, thus, should be "I will..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let you hear the new version of Take it! Sailor Uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So look forward to it? {Is he really asking here?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't watch next week...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll turn into Mars and scold you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fumoffu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We got pretty into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's ordered a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it your turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is when you're supposed to order a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't choose one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one should I do? {Use "sing" instead of "do"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.72,0:21:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also a menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. {added - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can also eat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That song totally broke my flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Should have saved it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What flow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How you sometimes feel like you sing better?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder if I can sing this.
