Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:28.80,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,There's a tambourine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.80,0:22:31.42,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,We can play it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.42,0:22:32.16,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:33.75,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Try this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.75,0:22:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.17,0:22:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a hardcore anime song will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.93,0:22:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I ordered an exciting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.48,0:23:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.81,0:23:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When something has completely outstripped the competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...and stands heads above the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.99,0:23:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...we use the word dantotsu to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's apparently short for danzen (on the very) top.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This word first appeared in literature...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...after the recent city election...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...where that person won by a landslide...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.58,0:23:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...on the very top.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.30,0:23:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Savory Day."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to next time!
